%% Diagram: Idempotent webhook consumer state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Received: HTTP POST + signature
    Received --> Rejected: Bad signature / replay window expired
    Received --> Deduped: event_id already processed
    Received --> Locked: SETNX event_id lock
    Locked --> Applied: Mutation succeeds
    Locked --> Retrying: Transient failure (5xx / timeout)
    Locked --> Failed: Permanent failure (4xx / schema)
    Retrying --> Locked: Backoff (exponential, capped)
    Retrying --> DLQ: Max attempts exceeded
    Applied --> [*]
    Deduped --> [*]: Return 200 (no-op)
    Failed --> DLQ
    DLQ --> Investigated: On-call replay / manual ledger
    Investigated --> Locked
    Rejected --> [*]: 401 / drop
